1
00:00:32,780 --> 00:00:35,860
=Fate of Beauty=

2
00:00:36,060 --> 00:00:38,940
=Episode 24=
(Begin Anew)

3
00:00:39,032 --> 00:00:40,360
(Taiji Hall)
An announcement is made

4
00:00:40,360 --> 00:00:41,770
After the investigation,

5
00:00:41,790 --> 00:00:42,999
the accusation of treason

6
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:45,149
against General Xia'an

7
00:00:45,150 --> 00:00:48,149
was found to be a slander
by the Crown Prince and his clique.

8
00:00:48,150 --> 00:00:49,650
By decree of His Majesty,

9
00:00:49,670 --> 00:00:51,069
the Crown Prince is to be deposed,

10
00:00:51,070 --> 00:00:53,140
and his clique arrested.

11
00:00:53,150 --> 00:00:54,580
From this day forth,

12
00:00:54,640 --> 00:00:56,749
the name of General Xia'an's daughter,

13
00:00:56,750 --> 00:00:58,900
Xia'an Le, will be resumed.

14
00:00:59,110 --> 00:00:59,999
Xiao Muran

15
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:01,580
has made contributions
to the investigation.

16
00:01:01,640 --> 00:01:03,749
He will be conferred
the title of General Wei.

17
00:01:03,750 --> 00:01:05,730
That's all.

18
00:01:06,940 --> 00:01:13,360
(Jiuyao Gate)

19
00:01:35,590 --> 00:01:37,200
Why are you leaving
without saying anything?

20
00:01:46,040 --> 00:01:47,500
No matter who loses this time,

21
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:50,370
we all will die.

22
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:52,170
This time,

23
00:01:53,590 --> 00:01:55,170
we must win.

24
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:08,860
Everything

25
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:11,580
is over.

26
00:02:15,347 --> 00:02:17,490
But it's just a beginning for us.

27
00:02:28,590 --> 00:02:30,140
Here we are now.

28
00:02:32,190 --> 00:02:34,210
I'm confused about who I am,

29
00:02:37,430 --> 00:02:38,980
let alone what "us"

30
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,980
or "beginning" are.

31
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:46,100
I need time

32
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:49,100
to forget everything about Ban Meng.

33
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:52,610
Please forget

34
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:58,260
about Ban Meng.

35
00:02:58,300 --> 00:03:00,499
♪The wind blows♪

36
00:03:00,500 --> 00:03:02,459
♪The shadow of the flowers♪

37
00:03:02,460 --> 00:03:05,000
♪Are swaying...♪

38
00:03:05,910 --> 00:03:07,890
What if I can't?

39
00:03:08,100 --> 00:03:10,099
♪Will listen♪

40
00:03:10,100 --> 00:03:13,000
♪To me?♪

41
00:03:13,380 --> 00:03:15,979
♪This is♪

42
00:03:15,980 --> 00:03:18,019
♪A dream♪

43
00:03:18,020 --> 00:03:19,629
♪Yet to awaken...♪

44
00:03:19,630 --> 00:03:20,610
Let's consider

45
00:03:21,870 --> 00:03:23,579
our encounter a dream.

46
00:03:23,580 --> 00:03:25,880
♪Your...♪

47
00:03:26,630 --> 00:03:28,140
Now, the dream is over.

48
00:03:29,380 --> 00:03:31,499
♪Walking through♪

49
00:03:31,500 --> 00:03:33,760
♪Streets...♪

50
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,860
Go and live your life.

51
00:03:37,340 --> 00:03:39,680
♪Why...♪

52
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,379
What about yours?

53
00:03:41,380 --> 00:03:44,120
♪Alone?♪

54
00:03:45,180 --> 00:03:47,299
♪Love♪

55
00:03:47,300 --> 00:03:49,320
♪Clings on like an illness...♪

56
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:52,029
The lives of Ban Meng and Xia'an Le

57
00:03:52,030 --> 00:03:53,700
are long gone.

58
00:03:56,740 --> 00:03:59,280
♪Are the hardest to say...♪

59
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:00,770
As for mine,

60
00:04:00,980 --> 00:04:03,800
♪No one should be blamed...♪

61
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:06,700
I don't know.

62
00:04:07,260 --> 00:04:10,579
♪But not letting go♪

63
00:04:10,580 --> 00:04:15,680
♪When they should let go♪

64
00:04:16,180 --> 00:04:20,179
♪Having you♪

65
00:04:20,180 --> 00:04:24,360
♪And losing you at the same time♪

66
00:04:25,420 --> 00:04:28,499
♪A heavy raindrop♪

67
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:31,939
♪Falls from my eye♪

68
00:04:31,940 --> 00:04:36,339
♪This isn't proof of my love for you♪

69
00:04:36,340 --> 00:04:39,520
♪Just the pain in my heart...♪

70
00:04:41,830 --> 00:04:42,930
Why are you standing here?

71
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:45,610
Go!

72
00:04:55,140 --> 00:04:59,004
♪I love you♪

73
00:04:59,005 --> 00:05:03,105
♪But I have to lose you…♪

74
00:05:03,830 --> 00:05:04,690
(Yeting,)

75
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:07,020
(let me tell you a secret.)

76
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,610
I realize

77
00:05:11,430 --> 00:05:13,340
that I'm in love with Ban Meng.

78
00:05:13,580 --> 00:05:18,619
♪Will you watch how I end♪

79
00:05:18,620 --> 00:05:22,400
♪Or remember me?♪

80
00:05:22,420 --> 00:05:26,200
♪Even if it's only...♪

81
00:05:42,870 --> 00:05:44,250
You won this time.

82
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:48,660
It's time to learn to behave

83
00:05:50,190 --> 00:05:51,540
and love her wholeheartedly.

84
00:05:54,380 --> 00:05:57,720
♪In the dreams♪

85
00:06:01,140 --> 00:06:01,869
(Three years later)

86
00:06:01,870 --> 00:06:02,980
Young Lady!

87
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,220
Young Lady.

88
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:10,829
Why the rush?

89
00:06:10,830 --> 00:06:11,930
What has happened?

90
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:14,479
Second Young Master quelled
the rebellion at the southwest border

91
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:15,509
and won the battle.

92
00:06:15,510 --> 00:06:17,250
He's leading the troop
back to the capital today.

93
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:18,949
I wonder

94
00:06:18,950 --> 00:06:20,540
if you and he will get to meet.

95
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:21,810
Talkative.

96
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,239
(Miss,)

97
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:47,810
(may I hide here for a while?)

98
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:49,780
(I'm doomed)

99
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:51,810
(if my brother finds me.)

100
00:06:56,430 --> 00:06:57,269
(My name is)

101
00:06:57,270 --> 00:06:58,460
(Xiao Muran.)

102
00:06:58,630 --> 00:06:59,860
(For what happened earlier today,)

103
00:07:00,310 --> 00:07:01,170
(I will)

104
00:07:01,310 --> 00:07:03,300
(take the responsibility.)

105
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,130
(Smile more.)

106
00:07:10,310 --> 00:07:11,730
(All the flowers in this garden)

107
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:13,930
(pale in comparison to your smile.)

108
00:08:32,580 --> 00:08:35,379
♪The rain that falls over♪

109
00:08:35,380 --> 00:08:37,320
♪The green hills♪

110
00:08:37,420 --> 00:08:39,899
♪Is vaguely blown♪

111
00:08:39,900 --> 00:08:41,840
♪Into my dreams♪

112
00:08:42,060 --> 00:08:44,499
♪I'm leaning on you♪

113
00:08:44,500 --> 00:08:46,800
♪For a moment♪

114
00:08:47,100 --> 00:08:49,040
♪Of refuge♪

115
00:08:51,580 --> 00:08:54,219
♪I'm afraid that if my beautiful dream♪

116
00:08:54,220 --> 00:08:56,160
♪Fades away♪

117
00:08:56,300 --> 00:09:00,539
♪I'll wake up♪

118
00:09:00,540 --> 00:09:08,320
♪Alone in a long silence♪

119
00:09:10,260 --> 00:09:12,699
♪To love or to hate♪

120
00:09:12,700 --> 00:09:15,139
♪I can't help it♪

121
00:09:15,140 --> 00:09:17,579
