128
00:09:38,860 --> 00:09:42,219
♪I'll end up scattered in the mud♪

129
00:09:42,220 --> 00:09:47,739
♪I can't bear to see the wind
blow against you♪

130
00:09:47,740 --> 00:09:53,120
♪Maybe by hiding my heart♪

131
