132
00:09:58,220 --> 00:10:01,419
♪Lying to you that my love for you♪

133
00:10:01,420 --> 00:10:07,360
♪Is only one ten-thousandth♪

134
00:10:07,580 --> 00:10:10,019
♪Rain from the bygone past♪

135
00:10:10,020 --> 00:10:11,680
♪Falls♪

136
00:10:12,340 --> 00:10:14,899
♪It's blown♪

137
00:10:14,900 --> 00:10:16,840
♪Into my dreams once again♪

138
00:10:16,980 --> 00:10:19,520
♪How should I choose?♪

139
00:10:19,620 --> 00:10:24,480
